      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I'm not sure I understand the concept of \"drift\" or how my responses are supposed to be biased. I'm a large language model, my responses are generated based on patterns in the data I was trained on, and I strive to provide accurate and informative answers. I'm not aware of any \"interpretive\" viewpoints I've given that could be considered subjective or biased. Can you explain what you mean by \"subjective qualitative assessments\" and how they're supposed to be pruned?",
